‘O Johann Sebastian Bach ka haku mele Kelemania a me ka mea ʻokana i kākau i nā hana no‘eau no ka papa hīmeni, no ka hui hoʻokani pila, a me no nā mea pa‘ahana.

‘O Ludwig van Beethoven (‘ōlelo Pelekania: ˈlʊdvɪg væn ˈbeɪtoʊvən. ‘ōlelo Kelemānia: ˈluːtvɪç fan ˈbeːthoːfn, 16 Kekemapa 1770 – 26 Malaki 1827) ka haku mele Kelemānia ame ka mea piano.

ʻO Richard Milhous Nixon, hānau ʻia ʻo Ianuali 9, 1913 ma Yorba Linda ma ʻAmelika Hui Pū ʻIa ʻo ia ka 36th Hope Pelekikena o ʻAmelika Hui Pū ʻIa mai Ianuali 20, 1953 a Ianuali 20, 1961 a laila ka 37th Pelekikena o ʻAmelika Hui Pū ʻIa, mai Ianuali 20, 1969 a ʻAukake 9 1974.

ʻO George Herbert Walker Bush, hānau ʻia ma Iune 12, 1924 ma Milton, ʻAmelika Hui Pū ʻIa, ʻo ia ka Hope Pelekikena mai ka makahiki 1981 a i ka 1989 a me ka Pelekikena o ʻAmelika Hui Pū ʻIa mai ka makahiki 1989 a hiki i ka makahiki 1993.
